title: More Or Less?
description:
Tony Kornheiser and Michael Wilbon discuss if the US Open is more or less interesting now that Serena and Nadal have been eliminated, what the biggest result from college football this weekend was and if Dustin Johnson’s win at the LIV Tour event this weekend was a big moment.
